{"tid":1826644,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得中國情形同當年既日本驚人地相似","createTime":"2020-01-16T09:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T13:25:49.000Z","uid":63331,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d04ec0ad7f6ad6fea7f9bb9eac4a21498fb9de47","tid":1826644,"uid":63331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T09:52:12.000Z","msg":"大家都係三四十年間經濟急速發展，去到世界第二水平令美國佬覺得自己地位受挑戰，要打貿易戰解決<br />\n個陣日本同樣食住人口紅利期既優勢，同埋國內財團放寬信貸補貼國內產業<br />\n而中國就係靠國家補貼<br />\n不過日本係自家品牌橫掃全球，中國就係負責幫全球代工<br />\n去到貿易戰開打咁岩都係人口紅利期即將結束<br />\n依家美國不停打擊中國既生產線，迫d企業轉去東南亞同當年打壓日本出口既效果一樣<br />\n再見到中國被剔出匯率操縱國之後人民幣升值<br />\n即刻諗起廣場協定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過依家無當年直接大幅干預咁癲<br />\n<br />\n1985年後日本依照廣場協定大幅升值日元，導致出口產業失去競爭力而倒閉，或人力需求較大的勞動製造業外移，而進口產業卻因貨幣購買力增強而受益，對於日本這樣物資急需進口的國家來說，短期之內出現了一波榮景，因為多數人購買進口商品的購買力增強，但之後卻是經濟崩盤。 From wiki <a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%97%A5%E5%85%83%E5%8D%87%E5%80%BC%E8%95%AD%E6%A2%9D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%258D%2587%25E5%2580%25BC%25E8%2595%25AD%25E6%25A2%259D&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=4adada40\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%97%A5%E5%85%83%E5%8D%87%E5%80%BC%E8%95%AD%E6%A2%9D</a><br />\n<br />\n依家中國都係急需大豆同豬肉呢d農產品，黎緊仲要買2000億(假設佢唔反口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n個陣日本因為咁搞到個經濟泡沫勁大，最後一發不可收拾<br />\n依家中國本身個泡沫都好大通漲又勁，地方政府仲周身債<br />\n好似仲衰過當年日本<br />\n仲有就係兩次都係萊特希澤做代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb81f002009322bfd7e1bba98b76af2ee5be7cd","tid":1826644,"uid":4258,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T09:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d883d2d555368a067623086ad6469f869766ab","tid":1826644,"uid":264121,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由高登吹到連登既支爆今次真係近了"},{"pid":"f08d7d9f13e292ffd1e587bb97e2a27a7bdcb4b5","tid":1826644,"uid":22422,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"唔似囉ok?<br />\n起碼日本嘅工業技術 科技都係真嘅"},{"pid":"a51b5cce3a463845ef541f0b41569345d7710732","tid":1826644,"uid":77416,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"人地日本只係經濟gg 政府冇倒台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以中共應該會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b8d83af7a1d21c5da8dbd77607b588d2f617e7","tid":1826644,"uid":34804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"唔同，中國經濟已經進入衰退。"},{"pid":"629e75a59de4cb3fb17e856c9313952c5c283a91","tid":1826644,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:30:08.000Z","msg":"其實並唔相似<br />\n<br />\n支那注定死得更慘"},{"pid":"e6decf3e51fdec755cac36c08a7f03cc0e4d6bbd","tid":1826644,"uid":75072,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"日本到達停滯時期已經係發達國家，支那有排都未撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31565ee25f9a5f12dc6a4eb4c9909f807812ae8","tid":1826644,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a51b5cce3a463845ef541f0b41569345d7710732","tid":1826644,"uid":77416,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"人地日本只係經濟gg 政府冇倒台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以中共應該會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:45:18.000Z","msg":"咁因為日本人可以選舉..."},{"pid":"39a3160cdebe0f32a4abcf80ae46f05d56d93f0a","tid":1826644,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a31565ee25f9a5f12dc6a4eb4c9909f807812ae8"